            name (which is a provider name or healthcare organization name) —  DR. PETER TAI-CHING HO  M.D., PH.D.. Records indicate that the provider gender is "Male". 
            The enumeration date of this NPI Number is 09/17/2006. NPI Number information was last updated on 07/08/2007.
        
