                                                    8:30 AM ET 06/15/2017
                                                


PALM BEACH, Florida, June 15, 2017 Clinical Trials for orphan drugs have shown tremendous potential in diagnosis and treatment of cancer with an increase in indications to treat an array of different diseases such as lymphoma, leukemia, myeloma, and others to boost the market growth potential for biotechs and pharmaceutical companies alike.

















